adithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32472,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/tawbah-bidah-innovation\/","url_meta":{"origin":27026,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bid\u2019ah: Repentance not accepted until heresy abandoned","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah veils repentance from the practitioner of any heresy.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 4204 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36653,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/21\/umar-tawbatan-nasuhan\/","url_meta":{"origin":27026,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Tawbah: The meaning of sincere repentance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: I asked Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, about His saying, \u201cRepent to Allah with sincere repentance,\u201d (66:8). Umar said, \u201cIt is a servant w